{"id": 2753, "genre": 1000, "title": "评分网站上不成文的「得分定律」，你觉得哪个是真实的？", "description": "《各大评分网站得分一点通》", "record_count": 12133, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190122093218qXBQ920GaiSDujyW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-27T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5271, "title": "评分网站上不成文的「得分定律」，你觉得哪个是真实的？", "content": "评分网站上的哪些不成文的「得分定律」，你觉得哪个是真实的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 323773, "content": "贴金定律，越是号称“中国版XX/古装版XX”的分数越低", "image": "img/option/option/20190122093954IGPQ6pSH3W8o5NEs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323774, "content": "定语定律，“国产奇幻悬疑爆笑巨制”定语越长分数越低", "image": "img/option/option/201901220941259TFsoB3GXl6I450Q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323775, "content": "格调定律，喜剧/恐怖片容易被打低分，文艺/励志相反", "image": "img/option/option/20190122094307zCSqT62lL1fashG5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323776, "content": "贺岁定律，集结一堆过气明星的港产贺岁喜剧都是低分", "image": "img/option/option/20190122094418NGfimOplVnPceXz1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323778, "content": "综艺定律，综艺改编电影就是低分保证", "image": "img/option/option/20190122095504kA8O7Ra4GEQxqIco.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323779, "content": "流量定律，含小鲜肉的排行榜由粉丝经济能力决定排名", "image": "img/option/option/20190122095632lt3nx0GXj96pBDHO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323771, "content": "页数定律，越厚的书评分越高，全集总比单册分高", "image": "img/option/option/20190122093529Nkq8g3LwI0QEntBi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323772, "content": "谐音定律，越喜欢在书名/片名用谐音梗的分数越低", "image": "img/option/option/201901220936323l7FeZOLyqRPIgNH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}